					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Edit: oops, I hit reply here instead of new post. My bad!</p> <p>I was wary of the premise at first, seeming more like an extended gag than a real premise, but you fleshed it out surprisingly well. My only issue is the use of &quot;snek&quot; which, while being adorable, sort of breaks the flow. It would have been just as effective without the &quot;snake = snek&quot; portions, in my opinion. Still, this was short, sweet, and very enjoyable. +1</p> 
